<p>And don't miss <strong>the latest updates from the people making WordPress</strong>. We've got you covered with <a href="https://poststatus.com/make-wordpress/">This Week at WordPress.org</a>. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/2699.png" alt="‚öô" class="wp-smiley" /></p>
